body:
Select      OM.ITObjectName, OMV.ITObjectName DataSetITObjectName, S.ScreenID, S.ScreenCaption, DS.ScreenID DetayScreenID, DS.ScreenCaption DetayScreenCaption,
            OVI.VeriIslemAdi, OM.ITObjectAlias, ADDD.AnalizDataID, DADD.AnalizDataID DetayAnalizDataID
From        IT15_ObjectsVeriIslemleri OVI
            Inner Join IT15_ObjectsM OM On OM.ITObjectID = OVI.SPITObjectID
            Inner Join IT15_ObjectsM OMV On OMV.ITObjectID = OVI.ITObjectID
            Left Outer Join IT15_Screens S On S.ITObjectID = OMV.ITObjectID
            Left Outer Join IT15_Screens DS On DS.ITObjectID2 = OMV.ITObjectID
            Left Outer Join IT15_AnalizDataD ADDD On ADDD.TSDatasetID = OMV.ITObjectID
            Left Outer Join IT15_AnalizDataD DADD On DADD.TSDetayDatasetID = OMV.ITObjectID
Where       OVI.VeriIslemAdi <> OM.ITObjectAlias And OM.ITType = 3
Order By    OM.ITObjectID, OVI.ITVeriIslemID
